name: RestaurantFinder
0:
”Alexa, open restaurant finder and find open restaurants around 94043”
”Alexa, open restaurant finder and get open restaurants around 95008”
”Alexa, open restaurant finder and find open restaurants near 95050”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: restaurant finder
des:
[1] The purpose of this skill is to search for open restaurants around a given neighborhood by specifying the corresponding zip code. 
[2] It fetches and outputs three restaurants entries ranked by distance along with the address.
[3] Currently, this skill is limited to 5 digit United States zip codes only.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
